%T A007985 5632662,16408866,47875650,139908774,409404630,1199368026,3517351890,
%U A007985 10325547582,30339113718,89217594738,262561101282,773248631222,2278737199606
%N A007985 Co-growth function of the group < a, b, a^{-1}, b^{-1} | b >, isomorphic to Z (counting only reduced words).
%H A007985 Stephen P Humphries, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1017/S030500419600134X">Cogrowth of groups and the Dedekind-Frobenius group determinant</a>, Mathematical Proceeding of the Cambridge Philosophical Society volume 121 Part 2 pages 193-217 (1997).
%F A007985 G.f.: (x+1) * sqrt(1-x) / sqrt((1-3*x) * (3*x^2+1)) [from Humphries]. - _Sean A. Irvine_, Feb 26 2018
%F A007985 D-finite with recurrence n*a(n) +(-3*n+1)*a(n-1) +2*(n+1)*a(n-2) -6*n*a(n-3) +3*(-n+6)*a(n-4) +9*(n-5)*a(n-5)=0. - _R. J. Mathar_, Aug 15 2025
%e A007985 Let A = a^_{-1}, B = b^{-1}. a(4) counts strings on a,A,b,B of length 4 that are reduced (no aA, Aa, bB, Bb) and have the same number of A's and a's. These are:
%e A007985   bbbb, BBBB, abbA, aBBA, Abba, ABBa,
%e A007985   abAb, abAB, aBAb, aBAB, babA, baBA, BabA, BaBA,
%e A007985   Abab, AbaB, ABab, ABaB, bAba, bABa, BAba, BABa.
%K A007985 nonn,changed
%O A007985 1,1
%A A007985 _Stephen P. Humphries_
%E A007985 More terms from _Sean A. Irvine_, Feb 26 2018
%E A007985 Name clarified by _Andrei Zabolotskii_, Apr 29 2026
